snippet.title: Diana and Roma explore the Professions of the Future
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma press colored buttons, enter the future and explore Professions. Acquaintance of children with different professions develops erudition, awareness and increases motivation for story role-playing games. Diana and Roma will show what a designer of clothes for pets, a roboticist, a manager of space tourism, an ecological architect, a blogger, a 3D modeler, a biologist, a programmer and сleaner.
Thanks for watching!
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
